{"tid":357622,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪五日四夜 有經驗人士入黎","createTime":"2017-08-13T05:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T17:37:46.000Z","uid":19834,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2721eb73e2db129bd0a38a6987785fa7ccfe068","tid":357622,"uid":19834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"下個月會同老婆去大阪玩五日<br />\n<br />\n由於第一次去 可能會較多問題<br />\n<br />\n我係早機去 黃昏機返<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 應該三點左右到機場 跟住直接去難波check in<br />\n我諗搞好哂D野 應該五點六點左右 <br />\n第一晚可能就係心齋橋 食野行下就算<br />\n<br />\nDay 2: 去京都 睇下風景 寺廟 夜晚都係返酒店附近食野行下<br />\n<br />\nDay3:去奈良撚鹿 <br />\n<br />\nDay4:去環球影城 <br />\n<br />\nDay5:黑門市場 行下街就走<br />\n<br />\n我咁既街程有無問題<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 去完奈良可以去邊<br />\n<br />\n我Usj 個到 買快證7 定買快證4 已經夠？<br />\n<br />\n我會買埋vip入場卷 <br />\n<br />\n搭車我係咪一張ic卡就夠？<br />\n<br />\n唔太熟日本<br />\n<br />\n利申：同老婆窮遊 求助"},{"pid":"6782196528a8b64c61101b3169330b70f0cfe8c4","tid":357622,"uid":66423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"Usj就用錢買時間<br />\n我買左5"},{"pid":"c022b486e76932363b2c00685a16bea84c5aac53","tid":357622,"uid":66423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Usj就用錢買時間<br />\n我買左4</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a308dcfa34fd0f51ead2d8366dfbd6e134770bb3","tid":357622,"uid":19834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Usj就用錢買時間<br />\n我買左4</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快證7 連埋所有入場卷 要成1500<br />\n算唔算貴"},{"pid":"de3e83582b73d304d7290a6190f1e3cc8aa20f6f","tid":357622,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"打算窮遊就做多D功課用時間換金錢啦<br />\n<br />\nD3 加埋宇治"},{"pid":"a12b6ed10677e2f0f22ce35fade2b2bc1a88519d","tid":357622,"uid":30410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"book左酒店未？D2即日來回京都好晒時間"},{"pid":"f4c715f1c49e8c99c80bb5cedce7d152f3c3d8b7","tid":357622,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"你係香港都唔會兩個人share 一張八達通啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買多張啦<br />\n<br />\nday pass 又好，ic 咭又好。<br />\n<br />\n阿嫂鐘唔鐘意shopping? 預埋時間"},{"pid":"cff9bd02182af1eedb5ede22055f0d3dc8790723","tid":357622,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"奈良可以足一日"},{"pid":"56ca303f49a3fd11fb460bd4dbd1af3d567ac2d4","tid":357622,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奈良可以足一日</blockquote><br />\n去埋宇治都得"},{"pid":"f813c211b031976b97683b5f23b9bf944719c229","tid":357622,"uid":121328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半日都已經走得  <br />\n去宇治呀   憩靜既一個地方👍🏻"},{"pid":"09b9d00e93a60518290bd47fc840eaabeed82564","tid":357622,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半日都已經走得  <br />\n去宇治呀   憩靜既一個地方👍🏻</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我上次去 好多飛蟲"},{"pid":"ed287f90d8a11988e4e9a5e105723db03b7daff0","tid":357622,"uid":49035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半日都已經走得  <br />\n去宇治呀   憩靜既一個地方👍🏻</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我上次去 好多飛蟲</blockquote><br />\n去宇治要睇你既目的係乜<br />\n如果係綠茶加商店街就好撚多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去遠少少既地方就好靜好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40e0691f42aee83d136786912852732b0cd6b4c","tid":357622,"uid":121328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半日都已經走得  <br />\n去宇治呀   憩靜既一個地方👍🏻</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我上次去 好多飛蟲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得宇治較好   我最近去就冇咩蟲  都冇乜人   所以 唔錯   <br />\n但奈良去到真係唔想久留    好似好多野咬  又多人   啲鹿都幾可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說最後個日去臨城空outlet 行都係一個幾好嘅消遣地方.."},{"pid":"a834227190fe56c9b55375f2edd0549c8a298862","tid":357622,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T10:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>奈良可以足一日</blockquote><br />\n去埋宇治都得</blockquote><br />\n奈良慢行睇野仲好<br />\n宇治最好加伏見稻荷"},{"pid":"d2139e591b40fd61be1a17324b59808aeb813011","tid":357622,"uid":19834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:47:22.000Z","msg":"大阪 邊到多波鞋買？"},{"pid":"d609fce1543f224f047d9ad140d7f37d29b876ad","tid":357622,"uid":135118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大阪 邊到多波鞋買？</blockquote><br />\n心齋橋"},{"pid":"66d6b0a1f931967012b67d6b2c1baafe996b3327","tid":357622,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大阪 邊到多波鞋買？</blockquote><br />\n心齋橋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怕舊model 去rinku outlet, 買完去機場checkin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80afe5f76743c5eb15ae6e79606334feebf9e70","tid":357622,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n半日都已經走得  <br />\n去宇治呀   憩靜既一個地方👍🏻</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我上次去 好多飛蟲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得宇治較好   我最近去就冇咩蟲  都冇乜人   所以 唔錯   <br />\n但奈良去到真係唔想久留    好似好多野咬  又多人   啲鹿都幾可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說最後個日去臨城空outlet 行都係一個幾好嘅消遣地方..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾次去大阪都係去rinku outlet 做最後一站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7309d87a0098d2f81e9014ef1137afcf1a13d25a","tid":357622,"uid":136618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"心齋橋筋好大，可能你老婆行完後第二日會想再行，好多嘢買"},{"pid":"55a661d5310fb56c1cea8325cc506084a2a9164b","tid":357622,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:43:22.000Z","msg":"心齋橋D買衫,飾物嘅鋪頭,仲有龍蝦包之類嗰D小食,9點就收鋪<br />\n你晏晝5,6點先去+埋食飯應該唔夠時間"},{"pid":"491c0d8ead9d71c62604b65007c2bca98f6b5ba7","tid":357622,"uid":19834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"真心感激你地既回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我發覺日本D交通都幾複雜<br />\n<br />\n我需唔需要買pass呢<br />\n<br />\n定就咁用ic卡就夠"},{"pid":"7d5f463685b4fed340b0b8cb744482ea803bd3d2","tid":357622,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心感激你地既回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我發覺日本D交通都幾複雜<br />\n<br />\n我需唔需要買pass呢<br />\n<br />\n定就咁用ic卡就夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大阪你都係坐幾條線，好易。<br />\n<br />\n機場去難波可以坐南海電鐵，直到難波總站<br />\n<br />\n要唔要買pass?如果要去遠d 地方就抵，去大阪市內唔駛啦， iocca card 夠了"},{"pid":"0a0a249ae4610ba685a1cf656eae15f239fdd50e","tid":357622,"uid":64093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心感激你地既回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我發覺日本D交通都幾複雜<br />\n<br />\n我需唔需要買pass呢<br />\n<br />\n定就咁用ic卡就夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大阪你都係坐幾條線，好易。<br />\n<br />\n機場去難波可以坐南海電鐵，直到難波總站<br />\n<br />\n要唔要買pass?如果要去遠d 地方就抵，去大阪市內唔駛啦， iocca card 夠了</blockquote><br />\n搭單問 請問巴打如果我去埋京都嵐山睇紅葉加溫泉果d 應該買咩pass 最好？"},{"pid":"129d8882e1d5f506b2158144678a6740cdcdeabf","tid":357622,"uid":136618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心感激你地既回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過我發覺日本D交通都幾複雜</span><br />\n<br />\n我需唔需要買pass呢<br />\n<br />\n定就咁用ic卡就夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，之前去試過搭錯車，原來有啲站名一樣，好似「九條」呢啲，可能京都又有，大阪都有，最好睇清楚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07369b7a3610828c1e4db932b5c2b1ffc621880d","tid":357622,"uid":100635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:58:11.000Z","msg":"正常行程.正路冇伏"},{"pid":"c6da9f5db75d639e2c9e0ef26a5b2f2b1d0fedb8","tid":357622,"uid":31109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:09:53.000Z","msg":"我就海游館+動物園+奈良撚鹿放埋同一日<br />\n結論係動物園可以唔去都得"},{"pid":"c5e47fba7db6494735847be2f02db0faf25aef9b","tid":357622,"uid":119008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大阪 邊到多波鞋買？</blockquote><br />\n心齋橋</blockquote><br />\n美國村都有 不過好貴"},{"pid":"773fa92db838551dddcd8a0c97dd9b92e4ad05bd","tid":357622,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:13:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5510e6de1969c78a771afcbfde6f2a42ba259834","tid":357622,"uid":31109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就海游館+動物園+奈良撚鹿放埋同一日<br />\n結論係動物園可以唔去都得</blockquote><br />\n另外唔知你買左USJ EXPRESS PASS未<br />\n未的話最好快啲上官網睇下嗰幾日會唔會賣哂<br />\n我就臨去前三星期先睇 發現已經賣哂<br />\n最終就用一張門票窮遊USJ<br />\n<br />\n至於你問會唔會貴<br />\n貴就梗架啦 但學上面有位巴打所講<br />\n用錢買排隊時間<br />\n我排Minions 排左130分鐘左右<br />\n但有Pass可能快一倍"},{"pid":"f86765e65d69d6ed8